OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry
OL,6,Fovernight with variable amounts of
OL,7,Fcloud and lengthy clear spells
OL,8,Fdeveloping. Chilly with a risk of a
OL,9,Frural frost in the east. Turning
OL,10,Fcloudier across the northwest towards
OL,11,Fdawn. Mostly light and variable winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FCloudy with patchy rain
OL,14,Farriving across the region during the
OL,15,Fmorning. Turning drier and brighter
OL,16,Finto the afternoon with sunny spells
OL,17,Fdeveloping. Perhaps the odd isolated
OL,18,Fshower later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
